Frequently Asked Questions

Your trust is paramount. Here you will find the answers to the most frequently asked questions so you know exactly where you stand.

How quickly will I notice results?

Most users feel clear relief within 24–48 hours. For some, it takes a little longer, depending on the severity of the nerve pain. With daily use, the effects become stronger.

Is this product safe for long-term use?

Yes, it is developed with safe and skin-friendly ingredients and can be used daily. It is clinically tested and contains no harsh substances. Also suitable for sensitive skin.

Does this work differently than regular creams or gels?

Yes, the roll-on works deeper because the formula specifically supports circulation and nerve function. It not only addresses the pain but also helps reduce the underlying cause. That makes it more effective than superficial pain creams.

Who is this product suitable for?

It is suitable for anyone with burning pain, tingling, numbness, or cramps in the feet and legs. Also ideal for people with neuropathy due to age, strain, diabetes, or poor circulation. If you are in doubt, you can safely try it out thanks to the risk-free guarantee.

How do I use the roll-on for the best results?

Apply the gel twice a day to the feet and legs. Massage lightly so that the formula can absorb well. Consistent use yields the best and fastest results.
